item.title: Help please trying to change home!=(
item.dc:creator: @Dastan1 Dastan_
item.description:
@Dastan1 wrote:

to move npc’s around you can use autospawn.cfg
to move objects around you can use client.java search for

makeglobalobject

to change home teleport coordinates in your spell book or anywhere else use clickingMost.java
search for the current coordinates in there and change it
